item.title: Thrash Metal Catacombs
item.description:
Thrash Metal Catacombs

Thrash Metal Catacombs group has 381 members at Last.fm. Connected artists include Aftermath, PAPSMEAR, Battalion. The group embraces all forgotten and obscure thrash metal acts from the past and present days.
